# AI Transparency Statement

*Everything here is written by me.*

This doesn't mean I am necessarily anti-AI, but when I'm reading an article I would like to believe that the writer took their time to try and understand what they are writing about. I believe that means they respect the time the reader invest in reading, so I try to uphold that myself.

I've tried to use LLMs before for editing posts, but I found that it made the process boring and the end-result lacking my personality in it. I prefer to preserve my sometimes weird grammar, way of phrasing stuff and if I have mistakes so be it.

I *do*, however, use LLMs for brainstorming and finding references.
